game.name: Elsa And Anna Highschool Fashion
game.description:
Today, we have brought to you an exclusively designed new dressing game for girls from the popular Frozen games category. It is a wonderful time as the two cute princesses from Disney world have joined their high school. They look pretty excited, but the problem is that they are unable to choose the school uniform. Do you consider yourself as an excellent fashion stylist? Join Elsa And Anna Highschool Fashion game and be prepared to help the princesses to become a star in the high school!
There are different styles of clothes and accessories you find at her wardrobe. Browse through multiple outfit designs she can use during highschool in this free online html5 game! Try to put your best fashionable skills to dress them up perfectly and allow them to play with all their friends! These two lovely princesses rely on your talents, so do your best to help them to select the best-looking outfit.  Find wider outfit and accessory options for Elsa on the left side of the screen! 
Give her an option for top and bottom and then combine her dress with a nice pair of shoes, a matching school bag, a perfect glass as well as a pair of matching shocks! Once you are done with Elsa, make sure to do the same for Anna. After working on the looks of both the princesses, you can hit the right click button to see the final result. Good luck to create the best school uniform for both the princesses! Try more princess mobile games for kids that are playable on multiple devices on atmegame.com, no download required!
